column2: BRIEF-Biglari Holdings - Decided To Delay Annual Meeting Currently Scheduled For April 23, 2020 March 18 (Reuters) - Biglari Holdings Inc: * BIGLARI HOLDINGS - DECIDED TO DELAY ANNUAL MEETING CURRENTLY SCHEDULED FOR APRIL 23, 2020 * BIGLARI HOLDINGS - NOTICE WILL BE ISSUED NEXT MONTH AS TO NEW DATE OF MEETING AND WHETHER SHAREHOLDERS WILL BE ABLE TO ATTEND MEETING IN PERSON Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
